---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import salmaan from "../assets/images/salmaan_saeed.webp";
import linkedin from "../assets/icons/linkedin.webp";
import github from "../assets/icons/github.webp";
import wan_network from "../assets/images/wan_network_cisco_packet_tracer.webp";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const title = "Salmaan Saeed";
---

<Layout title={title}>
  <div class="mx-auto text-center">
    <p class="text-2xl font-bold mt-0">{title}</p>

    <p class="text-lg mb-2 mt-2">Alumni of NJIT</p>

    <p class="text-lg mb-2 mt-2">Contact & Profiles:</p>

    <div class="flex item-center justify-center">
      <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/sagedemage">
        <Image
          class="ml-0.5 mr-0.5 float-left"
          src={github}
          alt="my github profile"
          layout="constrained"
          width={35}
          height={35}
        />
      </a>

      <a
        target="_blank"
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/salmaan-saeed-6a5582197/"
      >
        <Image
          class="ml-0.5 mr-0.5 float-left"
          src={linkedin}
          alt="my linkedin profile"
          layout="constrained"
          width={35}
          height={35}
        />
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <Image
    class="mx-auto max-w-full h-auto block mt-2"
    src={salmaan}
    alt="Salmaan Saeed"
    layout="constrained"
    width={203}
    height={270}
  />

  <hr class="h-px my-8 bg-gray-300 border-0" />

  <p>
    Hi, my name is Salmaan Saeed. I'm an alumni of <b
      >New Jersey Institute of Technology</b
    >. I have a Bachelor of Science in <b>Information Technology</b>. I am
    interested in computer networking because I find it fascinating how
    computers and routers communicate with each other in a WAN. I have
    experience setting up a Kubernetes cluster with Docker. I learned about
    container orchestration and how it helps with the automation of deployment,
    management, and networking of containers. I took my time to learn about the
    architecture of a Kubernetes cluster. I have experience setting up the
    automation of Linux servers on virtual machines via Ansible. This project
    required me to setup port forwarding in order to access the virtual machines
    via SSH. I used my time to understand the networking of VirtualBox. My goal
    is to become a Desktop Support Technician. My long term goal is to become a
    Network Engineer.
  </p>

  <Image
    class="max-w-full h-auto"
    src={wan_network}
    alt="Salmaan Saeed WAN Network Cisco Packet Tracer"
    layout="constrained"
    width={950}
    height={576}
  />
</Layout>
